{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"WorkerGlobalScope.console","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/console","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><em><code>console</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/location\"><code>location</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/navigator\"><code>navigator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/self\"><code>self</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/dump\"><code>dump()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/importScripts\"><code>importScripts()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>イベント</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/error_event\"><code>error</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/languagechange_event\"><code>languagechange</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/offline_event\"><code>offline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/online_event\"><code>online</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Web Workers API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorker\"><code>ServiceWorker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorker\"><code>SharedWorker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>SharedWorkerGlobalScope</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Worker\"><code>Worker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerLocation\"><code>WorkerLocation</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerNavigator\"><code>WorkerNavigator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard warning\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>非標準:</strong> この機能は標準ではなく、標準化の予定もありません。公開されているウェブサイトには使用しないでください。ユーザーによっては使用できないことがあります。実装ごとに大きな差があることもあり、将来は振る舞いが変わるかもしれません。</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/console\"><code>Console</code></a> インターフェイスの読み取り専用 <code>console</code> プロパティは、ワーカーにブラウザコンソールへのアクセスを提供する <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/console\"><code>Console</code></a>&nbsp;オブジェクトを返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"構文","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> consoleObj <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>console<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"値","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/console\"><code>Console</code></a> オブジェクト</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>このプロパティはワーカー内でデバッグのためにブラウザコンソールへアクセスすることを可能にします。よって、例えばこのようにコールできます</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'test'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>inside a worker (which would basically be the equivalent of <code>self.console.log('test');</code>, as these are being called on the worker scope, which can be referenced with <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/self\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.self</code></a>), to return a test message out to the browser console.</p>\n\n<p>If you are calling <code>console.log()</code> from a <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope</code></a> or other worker scope that acts on a single loaded window, that tab's web console will receive the logs. However,&nbsp;If you are calling <code>console.log()</code> from a <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>SharedWorkerGlobalScope</code></a>, the global browser console will receive the logs.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications_2","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<p>仕様の一部ではありません。</p>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"api.WorkerGlobalScope.console","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"関連","title":"関連","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/console\"><code>Console</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"構文"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications_2"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連","id":"関連"}],"summary":"Console インターフェイスの読み取り専用 console プロパティは、ワーカーにブラウザコンソールへのアクセスを提供する Console オブジェクトを返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WorkerGlobalScope.console","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WorkerGlobalScope.console","locale":"fr","native":"Français"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/workerglobalscope/console","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/workerglobalscope/console/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope","title":"WorkerGlobalScope"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/console","title":"WorkerGlobalScope.console"}],"pageTitle":"WorkerGlobalScope.console - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}